      <ChildNodes>
        <Node ToolID="129">
          <GuiSettings Plugin="AlteryxGuiToolkit.TextBox.TextBox">
            <Position x="82" y="2118" width="864" height="144" />
          </GuiSettings>
          <Properties>
            <Configuration>
              <Text>Back to our Compliance Director. They have been sent the standardized performance figures for each of the departments they oversee, prior to bonuses being allocated.

They have asked for a reconciliation of the data from just the department that covers Tea &amp; Coffee; unfortunately this appears to be one of the un-named columns! Luckily the person who sent you the data mentioned that the Tea &amp; Coffee department were the only department to have an obvious skew to the results.

You are to provide:
    - summary statistics for the department (mean, median, maximum, minimum, and standard deviation)
    - a list of the 5 highest, and 10 lowest, performing regions for the Tea &amp; Coffee department

Create a workflow and ensure that you choose the correct data set!</Text>
              <Font name="Arial" size="8.25" style="0" />
              <TextColor name="Black" />
              <FillColor name="White" />
              <Shape shape="0" />
              <Justification Justification="0" />
            </Configuration>
            <Annotation DisplayMode="0">
              <Name />
              <DefaultAnnotationText />
              <Left value="False" />
            </Annotation>
          </Properties>
        </Node>
