          <Properties>
            <Configuration>
              <Text>The provided file has sales and inventory data for 5 store locations from November and December of 2022. The advertising department wants some figures for December for each store.

Create a workflow that will take the inventory data and produce the following 3 outputs. Match your solutions to the solution outputs provided. 
  
1.) Top 3 selling items from each store in December
2.) Bottom 2 selling items from each store in December
3.) All the items that either had no sales or ran out of stock in December

You be sure to add annotations to any tool that does not automatically produce them.</Text>
              <Font name="Arial" size="8.25" style="0" />
              <TextColor name="Black" />
              <FillColor name="White" />
              <Shape shape="0" />
              <Justification Justification="3" />
            </Configuration>
            <Annotation DisplayMode="0">
              <Name />
              <DefaultAnnotationText />
              <Left value="False" />
            </Annotation>
          </Properties>
        </Node>
